 abandonment recovery, A/B split testing, upsells, and more.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:50:\"https://www.learndash.com/integrations/thrivecart/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:45:\"learndash-thrivecart/learndash-thrivecart.php\";}i:16;a:16:{s:4:\"slug\";s:17:\"learndash-samcart\";s:4:\"kind\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:12:\"minimum_tier\";s:10:\"essentials\";s:7:\"top_dir\";s:17:\"learndash-samcart\";s:9:\"main_file\";s:21:\"learndash-samcart.php\";s:10:\"wporg_slug\";N;s:7:\"version\";s:7:\"1.1.0.1\";s:12:\"release_date\";s:10:\"2026-01-14\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:61:\"* Security - Tightened security around SamCart notifications.\";s:4:\"name\";s:29:\"LearnDash SamCart Integration\";s:11:\"description\";s:240:\"SamCart is a hosted shopping cart built by marketers, for marketers. It is optimized for conversions so as to increase your total revenue. This integration makes it possible to sell LearnDash courses with this high-converting shopping cart.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:47:\"https://www.learndash.com/integrations/samcart/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:39:\"learndash-samcart/learndash-samcart.php\";}i:17;a:16:{s:4:\"slug\";s:15:\"ld-multilingual\";s:4:\"kind\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:12:\"minimum_tier\";s:10:\"essentials\";s:7:\"top_dir\";s:15:\"ld-multilingual\";s:9:\"main_file\";s:19:\"ld-multilingual.php\";s:10:\"wporg_slug\";N;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.0.0\";s:12:\"release_date\";s:10:\"2022-03-28\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:133:\"* Feature - Initial release.\n* Tweak - View the full changelog [here](https://www.learndash.com/support/docs/add-ons/compatibility/).\";s:4:\"name\";s:34:\"LearnDash Multilingual Integration\";s:11:\"description\";s:167:\"This add-on allows for greater compatibility between LearnDash and multilingual sites that are using 3rd party plugins for administering the multilingual translations.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:76:\"https://learndash.com/support/kb/add-ons/compatibility-add-on/compatibility/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:35:\"ld-multilingual/ld-multilingual.php\";}i:18;a:16:{s:4:\"slug\";s:30:\"learndash-restrict-content-pro\";s:4:\"kind\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:12:\"minimum_tier\";s:10:\"essentials\";s:7:\"top_dir\";s:30:\"learndash-restrict-content-pro\";s:9:\"main_file\";s:34:\"learndash-restrict-content-pro.php\";s:10:\"wporg_slug\";N;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.1.2\";s:12:\"release_date\";s:10:\"2025-02-12\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:116:\"* Fix - Prevents a fatal error that could occur when creating a membership via the REST API in Restrict Content Pro.\";s:4:\"name\";s:42:\"LearnDash Restrict Content Pro Integration\";s:11:\"description\";s:364:\"Restrict Content Pro is a premium WordPress membership plugin designed for creating memberships and protecting your site content for paying members. With this integration you can create membership levels in Restrict Content Pro and then associate the membership levels to LearnDash courses. Customers are auto-enrolled into courses after signing-up for membership.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:60:\"https://www.learndash.com/integrations/restrict-content-pro/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:65:\"learndash-restrict-content-pro/learndash-restrict-content-pro.php\";}i:19;a:16:{s:4:\"slug\";s:19:\"learndash-gradebook\";s:4:\"kind\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:12:\"minimum_tier\";s:3:\"pro\";s:7:\"top_dir\";s:19:\"learndash-gradebook\";s:9:\"main_file\";s:23:\"learndash-gradebook.php\";s:10:\"wporg_slug\";N;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"4.4.0\";s:12:\"release_date\";s:10:\"2026-05-11\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:204:\"* Compatibility - LearnDash LMS 5.1.0 is now the minimum supported version.\n* Deprecate - Deprecated constants: `LEARNDASH_GRADEBOOK_LICENSING_CHECK_LICENSE_URL`, `LEARNDASH_GRADEBOOK_LICENSING_SITE_URL`.\";s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"Gradebook\";s:11:\"description\";s:208:\"Easily customize, track, and share scores with Gradebook. Explore student progression and scores in simple, flexible gradebook tables, and share individual scores and progress with students and their parents.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:49:\"https://www.learndash.com/gradebook-by-learndash/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:43:\"learndash-gradebook/learndash-gradebook.php\";}i:20;a:16:{s:4:\"slug\";s:15:\"learndash-notes\";s:4:\"kind\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:12:\"minimum_tier\";s:3:\"pro\";s:7:\"top_dir\";s:15:\"learndash-notes\";s:9:\"main_file\";s:27:\"learndash-student-notes.php\";s:10:\"wporg_slug\";N;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"2.1.0\";s:12:\"release_date\";s:10:\"2026-05-11\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:242:\"* Compatibility - LearnDash LMS 5.1.0 is now the minimum supported version.\n* Deprecate - Deprecated functions: `learndash_notes_check_auth_token`.\n* Fix - Resolved an issue where if LearnDash Core were deactivated, a fatal error would occur.\";s:4:\"name\";s:5:\"Notes\";s:11:\"description\";s:293:\"The Notes add-on makes note-taking simple and facilitates instructor communication when needed most, during the students study time. The Notes toolset is intuitive and flexible for students and provides an efficient, reliable, asynchronous workflow for instructors to answer student questions.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:45:\"https://www.learndash.com/notes-by-learndash/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:43:\"learndash-notes/learndash-student-notes.php\";}i:21;a:16:{s:4:\"slug\";s:18:\"learndash-propanel\";s:4:\"kind\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:12:\"minimum_tier\";s:3:\"pro\";s:7:\"top_dir\";s:18:\"learndash-propanel\";s:9:\"main_file\";s:22:\"learndash_propanel.php\";s:10:\"wporg_slug\";N;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"3.1.0\";s:12:\"release_date\";s:10:\"2026-05-11\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:289:\"* Compatibility - LearnDash LMS 5.1.0 is now the minimum supported version.\n* Deprecate - Deprecated classes: `LearnDashReportsLicensingAuthentication`, `LearnDashReportsLicensingMigration`.\n* Deprecate - Deprecated constants: `LDRP_LICENSING_CHECK_LICENSE_URL`, `LDRP_LICENSING_SITE_URL`.\";s:4:\"name\";s:8:\"ProPanel\";s:11:\"description\";s:289:\"ProPanel is a reporting add-on for LearnDash that you can buy separately. Once activated, it provides additional insights into your courses, such as revenue, user activity, quizzes, assignments, and more. It also includes a customizable front-end dashboard for easy access to your reports.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:48:\"https://www.learndash.com/propanel-by-learndash/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:41:\"learndash-propanel/learndash_propanel.php\";}i:22;a:16:{s:4:\"slug\";s:17:\"wdm-course-review\";s:4:\"kind\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:12:\"minimum_tier\";s:5:\"elite\";s:7:\"top_dir\";s:17:\"wdm-course-review\";s:9:\"main_file\";s:21:\"wdm-course-review.php\";s:10:\"wporg_slug\";N;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"2.3.0\";s:12:\"release_date\";s:10:\"2026-05-11\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:299:\"* Compatibility - LearnDash LMS 5.1.0 is now the minimum supported version.\n* Deprecate - Deprecated constants: `RRF_LICENSING_CHECK_LICENSE_URL`, `RRF_LICENSING_SITE_URL`.\n* Deprecate - Deprecated functions: `LearnDashReviews_PlusLicensingAuthentication`, `LearnDashReviews_PlusLicensingMigration`.\";s:4:\"name\";s:27:\"Ratings, Reviews & Feedback\";s:11:\"description\";s:179:\"The Ratings, Reviews, and Feedback Add-on gives you full control over the display of ratings and reviews, set custom templates, and make your courses better with student feedback.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0: