CENSING_CHECK_LICENSE_URL`, `WDM_LDGR_LICENSING_SITE_URL`.\";s:4:\"name\";s:18:\"Group Registration\";s:11:\"description\";s:75:\"Sell Group Licenses for Courses and Set Up Accounts for Learners in One Go.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:51:\"https://www.learndash.com/groups-management-add-on/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:47:\"ld-group-registration/ld-group-registration.php\";}i:25;a:16:{s:4:\"slug\";s:15:\"instructor-role\";s:4:\"kind\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:12:\"minimum_tier\";s:5:\"elite\";s:7:\"top_dir\";s:15:\"instructor-role\";s:9:\"main_file\";s:14:\"instructor.php\";s:10:\"wporg_slug\";N;s:7:\"version\";s:6:\"5.10.0\";s:12:\"release_date\";s:10:\"2026-05-11\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:329:\"* Compatibility - LearnDash LMS 5.1.0 is now the minimum supported version.\n* Deprecate - Deprecated constants: `INSTRUCTOR_ROLE_LICENSING_CHECK_LICENSE_URL`, `INSTRUCTOR_ROLE_LICENSING_SITE_URL`.\n* Deprecate - Deprecated functions: `LearnDashInstructor_RoleLicensingAuthentication`, `LearnDashInstructor_RoleLicensingMigration`.\";s:4:\"name\";s:15:\"Instructor Role\";s:11:\"description\";s:289:\"The Instructor Role gives you the power to add multiple course authors without compromising site security. Learn how you can leverage this powerful tool by creating roles with restricted back-end access to Course Authors, making content creation and management easier, and your site safer.\";s:8:\"category\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"authors\";a:1:{i:0;s:9:\"LearnDash\";}s:17:\"documentation_url\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:42:\"https://www.learndash.com/instructor-role/\";s:11:\"plugin_file\";s:30:\"instructor-role/instructor.php\";}}}}s:15:\"last_success_at\";i:1778657857;s:15:\"last_failure_at\";i:1778701094;s:10:\"last_error\";O:8:\"WP_Error\":3:{s:6:\"errors\";a:1:{s:42:\"lw-harbor-api-communications-not-permitted\";a:1:{i:0;s:52:\"External API communications have not been permitted.\";}}s:10:\"error_data\